<%# Open Source %>
<section class="mx-auto px-5 sm:px-0 max-w-xl my-12">
  <h2 class="text-xl text-balance font-medium text-stone-800 font-serif">Free &amp; Open Source</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-stone-600 text-balance">
    Free software is a matter of liberty, not price. We believe in building for a web that is open to all. Our software is open-source (AGPLv3), meaning you can self-host, modify, and even contribute back if you wish to.
  </p>
</section>

<%# Privacy %>
<section class="mx-auto px-5 sm:px-0 max-w-xl my-12">
  <h2 class="text-xl text-balance font-medium text-stone-800 font-serif">Privacy, no compromises</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 text-stone-600 text-balance">
    We don't track you or your subscribers. Your data stays private and secure on our servers, with no sharing or tracking involved. Your activities and information remain entirely yours.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-2 text-stone-600 text-balance">
    With us, you're automatically compliant with GDPR and other similar laws across the globe.
  </p>
</section>
